headline: Underground Line Replacement Enhances Service Reliability for JCP&L's Barrier Island Customers
summary: HOLMDEL, N.J. -- Jersey Central Power & Light , a subsidiary of FirstEnergy Corp. , is replacing an underwater, high-voltage power line to enhance service reliability to New Jersey's barrier islands....
